title: UC Davis offers WIC expertise as Congress considers funding (University of California - Davis)
text: ( Source : University of California - Davis ) As Congress prepares to consider reauthorization of the Healthy, Hunger-Free Kids Act , UC Davis Professor Marianne Page offers expertise on the act, which funds a number of nutrition programs,
